# multiple assignment = allows us to assign multiple vatiable at the same time in one line of code

# This is the normal way of assigning a value to a variable

name = "Norvin"
Age =  19
goodbehaviour = True 

print(name)
print(Age)
print(goodbehaviour)

# Application of Multiple assignment

name,Age,goodbehaviour = "Norvin", 19, True
'''The order of assigning variable sholud be in a sequential way.
. The order in which we are declaring the variables and order of assigning values to those variables should be same.'''

print(name)
print(Age)
print(goodbehaviour)
